<taxonomicName id="793AF470DDFB4F474685DCB1E8738D1F" authorityName="Casey" authorityYear="1918" class="Insecta" family="Carabidae" genus="Melomalus" higherTaxonomySource="GBIF" kingdom="Animalia" lsidName="" order="Coleoptera" pageId="431" pageNumber="432" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="genus">Melomalus</taxonomicName>
Casey, 1918: 37. Type species: 
<taxonomicName id="9A32B6931395709370C47EE9085A1269" class="Insecta" family="Carabidae" genus="Ochthedromus" higherTaxonomySource="GBIF" kingdom="Animalia" lsidName="" order="Coleoptera" pageId="431" pageNumber="432" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="species" species="planatus">
